title: Blunt.Talk.S01E02.WEBRip.x264-Abjex
description:
Walter Blunt is a British transplant intent on conquering the world of American cable news. Through the platform of his nightly interview show, Blunt is on a mission to impart his wisdom and guidance on how Americans should live, think and behave. Besieged by network bosses, a dysfunctional news staff, numerous ex-wives and children of all ages, Blunts only supporter is the alcoholic manservant he brought with him from the U.K. to join him in Los Angeles. The series follows the fallout from Blunts well-intentioned, but mostly misguided decision-making, both on and off the air
